<lb ed="X" n="0251c04"/><lb ed="R006" n="0180a07"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="36"><cb:jhead>大方廣佛新華嚴經合論卷第三十六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0251c05"/>
